Detailed Description

Set the display order of an field or property of an object. A field or property without an order defaults to order double.MaxValue. Each inheritance level receives its own order group.

Constructor & Destructor Documentation

Parameters
orderThe order in which to display this field or property. A field or property without an OrderAttribute defaults to order 0.
